<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/498534-i-m-looking-for-great-non-fiction-for">I&#39;m looking for great non-fiction for 16-18 year old readers in advanced classes--especially titles that have their literary fingers on the public pulse, so to speak. Should I consider this text for my students?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_498534'><a id="like_count_community_question_498534" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/498534?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">45 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F25489625-between-the-world-and-me">like</a></span>

