<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/12795515-laura-starks"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1490151301i/12795515._UX100_CR0,0,100,100_.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/12795515-laura-starks">Laura Starks</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Please do, I think it is very timely with what is happening in our country. It is an easy read, and I think will help your students gain some perspect<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Please do, I think it is very timely with what is happening in our country. It is an easy read, and I think will help your students gain some perspective on "black lives matter", and why that phrase is much more than "all lives matter".<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
