			<a class="actionLink" href="/topic/show/21744918-poll-ballot-between-the-world-and-me-by-ta-nehisi-coates---4-stars">[Poll Ballot] Between the World and Me by Ta-Nehisi Coates - 4 stars</a>
		</td>
		<td class="nobreak">
		  1
		  
		</td>
		<td>13</td>
		<td>Nov 02, 2020 09:27PM</td>
		<td>
				&nbsp;
		</td>
