	<tr>
		<td>
		    <b>
          <a title="Racial Justice Reading Group for White People" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/21510954-between-the-world-and-me-by-ta-nehisi-coates">Racial Justice Re...:</a>
        </b>
      
